      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 1,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) CORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z0f6aa3c63b0331881c8804e04e01ca5c\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z0f6aa3c63b0331881c8804e04e01ca5c\" data-section-id=\"Tmc6U10\" data-sememe-id=\"Mg1MDT0\">Bile acid diarrhea</a> occurs when <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Q60ukS&anker=Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-learningcard-id=\"Q60ukS\" data-anker=\"Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-section-id=\"2FcThV0\" data-sememe-id=\"QOXuHy\">bile acids</a>, normally reabsorbed in the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=xo0EVS&anker=Zce232f978ea5a8fb9edbb980a41502b8\" data-learningcard-id=\"xo0EVS\" data-anker=\"Zce232f978ea5a8fb9edbb980a41502b8\" data-section-id=\"h_ccLU0\">distal</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=eJ0xGS&anker=Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-learningcard-id=\"eJ0xGS\" data-anker=\"Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-section-id=\"FzcguU0\" data-sememe-id=\"w4chlc0\">ileum</a>, enter the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=R60lkS&anker=Ze19293358dc6c65dc95f936bb8fca493\" data-learningcard-id=\"R60lkS\" data-anker=\"Ze19293358dc6c65dc95f936bb8fca493\" data-section-id=\"K8cUnV0\" data-sememe-id=\"wPchSc0\">colon</a>, often after <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=eJ0xGS&anker=Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-learningcard-id=\"eJ0xGS\" data-anker=\"Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-section-id=\"FzcguU0\" data-sememe-id=\"w4chlc0\">ileal</a> resection. This patient, with a history of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VS0GA2&anker=Zef70853af5e87c95d210bf8df682f64c\" data-learningcard-id=\"VS0GA2\" data-anker=\"Zef70853af5e87c95d210bf8df682f64c\" data-sememe-id=\"I40YkT\">Crohn's disease</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=eJ0xGS&anker=Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-learningcard-id=\"eJ0xGS\" data-anker=\"Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-section-id=\"FzcguU0\" data-sememe-id=\"w4chlc0\">ileal</a> resection, likely experiences <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Za81182120613af86b266ff31432e241e\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Za81182120613af86b266ff31432e241e\" data-section-id=\"1mc2e10\" data-sememe-id=\"-SYDXK\">secretory diarrhea</a> due to unabsorbed <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Q60ukS&anker=Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-learningcard-id=\"Q60ukS\" data-anker=\"Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-section-id=\"2FcThV0\" data-sememe-id=\"QOXuHy\">bile acids</a> irritating the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=R60lkS&anker=Ze19293358dc6c65dc95f936bb8fca493\" data-learningcard-id=\"R60lkS\" data-anker=\"Ze19293358dc6c65dc95f936bb8fca493\" data-section-id=\"K8cUnV0\" data-sememe-id=\"wPchSc0\">colonic</a> <span data-sememe-id=\"Ze1Zxf0\">mucosa</span>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ym0nVg&anker=Z1de5d1df48f548f9d227c6743af88c42\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ym0nVg\" data-anker=\"Z1de5d1df48f548f9d227c6743af88c42\" data-section-id=\"oBX0b00\" data-sememe-id=\"cWYa4L\">Cholestyramine</a>, a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ym0nVg&anker=Zd31aed9f6080dcc1f0bd365755e8ed6c\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ym0nVg\" data-anker=\"Zd31aed9f6080dcc1f0bd365755e8ed6c\" data-section-id=\"oBX0b00\" data-sememe-id=\"yNbdd8\">bile acid sequestrant</a>, binds excess <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Q60ukS&anker=Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-learningcard-id=\"Q60ukS\" data-anker=\"Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-section-id=\"2FcThV0\" data-sememe-id=\"QOXuHy\">bile acids</a> in the intestine, reducing their irritative effect and alleviating <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-sememe-id=\"ro0fWS\">diarrhea</a>. This therapeutic approach is effective for managing <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z0f6aa3c63b0331881c8804e04e01ca5c\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z0f6aa3c63b0331881c8804e04e01ca5c\" data-section-id=\"Tmc6U10\" data-sememe-id=\"Mg1MDT0\">bile acid diarrhea</a> following <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=eJ0xGS&anker=Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-learningcard-id=\"eJ0xGS\" data-anker=\"Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-section-id=\"FzcguU0\" data-sememe-id=\"w4chlc0\">ileal</a> resection.<br><br><span class=\"wichtig\"><b>Key learning point: </b></span>Post-<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=eJ0xGS&anker=Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-learningcard-id=\"eJ0xGS\" data-anker=\"Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-section-id=\"FzcguU0\" data-sememe-id=\"w4chlc0\">ileal</a> resection <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-sememe-id=\"ro0fWS\">diarrhea</a> in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VS0GA2&anker=Zef70853af5e87c95d210bf8df682f64c\" data-learningcard-id=\"VS0GA2\" data-anker=\"Zef70853af5e87c95d210bf8df682f64c\" data-sememe-id=\"I40YkT\">Crohn's disease</a> patients is often due to <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Q60ukS&anker=Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-learningcard-id=\"Q60ukS\" data-anker=\"Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-section-id=\"2FcThV0\" data-sememe-id=\"QOXuHy\">bile acid</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=0S0ey2&anker=Zae07822252537d684eeec3f2d4ba9adb\" data-learningcard-id=\"0S0ey2\" data-anker=\"Zae07822252537d684eeec3f2d4ba9adb\" data-sememe-id=\"n407PT\">malabsorption</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Ym0nVg&anker=Z1de5d1df48f548f9d227c6743af88c42\" data-learningcard-id=\"Ym0nVg\" data-anker=\"Z1de5d1df48f548f9d227c6743af88c42\" data-section-id=\"oBX0b00\" data-sememe-id=\"cWYa4L\">cholestyramine</a> is an effective treatment for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z0f6aa3c63b0331881c8804e04e01ca5c\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z0f6aa3c63b0331881c8804e04e01ca5c\" data-section-id=\"Tmc6U10\" data-sememe-id=\"Mg1MDT0\">bile acid diarrhea</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=eS0xA2&anker=Z99af359a2a03545638a15b1bf2ae4096\" data-learningcard-id=\"eS0xA2\" data-anker=\"Z99af359a2a03545638a15b1bf2ae4096\" data-section-id=\"yw0dlR\" data-sememe-id=\"R80lm3\">Mesalamine</a> is used for its anti-inflammatory properties in active <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VS0GA2&anker=Zef70853af5e87c95d210bf8df682f64c\" data-learningcard-id=\"VS0GA2\" data-anker=\"Zef70853af5e87c95d210bf8df682f64c\" data-sememe-id=\"I40YkT\">Crohn's disease</a>. This patient shows no active inflammation on <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=T806N3&anker=Za4aebc8baa131b83620292e8d0363739\" data-learningcard-id=\"T806N3\" data-anker=\"Za4aebc8baa131b83620292e8d0363739\" data-sememe-id=\"nWb7Ns\">colonoscopy</a>, and the absence of blood or mucus in the stool and stable weight suggest the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-sememe-id=\"ro0fWS\">diarrhea</a> is not due to an inflammatory process. Increasing <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=eS0xA2&anker=Z99af359a2a03545638a15b1bf2ae4096\" data-learningcard-id=\"eS0xA2\" data-anker=\"Z99af359a2a03545638a15b1bf2ae4096\" data-section-id=\"yw0dlR\" data-sememe-id=\"R80lm3\">mesalamine</a> would not address <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Q60ukS&anker=Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-learningcard-id=\"Q60ukS\" data-anker=\"Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-section-id=\"2FcThV0\" data-sememe-id=\"QOXuHy\">bile acid</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=0S0ey2&anker=Zae07822252537d684eeec3f2d4ba9adb\" data-learningcard-id=\"0S0ey2\" data-anker=\"Zae07822252537d684eeec3f2d4ba9adb\" data-sememe-id=\"n407PT\">malabsorption</a>, the likely cause of the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-sememe-id=\"ro0fWS\">diarrhea</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=mm0VTg&anker=Z0d92af1eab239465721da02549c61854\" data-learningcard-id=\"mm0VTg\" data-anker=\"Z0d92af1eab239465721da02549c61854\" data-section-id=\"cubaJv\" data-sememe-id=\"yOadEk\">Empiric antibiotics</a> are considered for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=z80r63&anker=Z9aa32f677362a235a8ae39e011711f1b\" data-learningcard-id=\"z80r63\" data-anker=\"Z9aa32f677362a235a8ae39e011711f1b\" data-sememe-id=\"yzYdv7\">small intestinal bacterial overgrowth</a> (<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=z80r63&anker=Z9aa32f677362a235a8ae39e011711f1b\" data-learningcard-id=\"z80r63\" data-anker=\"Z9aa32f677362a235a8ae39e011711f1b\" data-sememe-id=\"yzYdv7\">SIBO</a>) or infection, especially with symptoms like <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j50_Pg&anker=Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-learningcard-id=\"j50_Pg\" data-anker=\"Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-sememe-id=\"CL0q-g\">fever</a> or abdominal <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=xN0EWg&anker=Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-learningcard-id=\"xN0EWg\" data-anker=\"Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-section-id=\"NBX-a00\">pain</a>. This patient has chronic <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z16ed63f1f94f558cfbffed53ce14a7fb\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z16ed63f1f94f558cfbffed53ce14a7fb\" data-section-id=\"1mc2e10\">watery diarrhea</a> without systemic infection signs, and negative <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z6dddefa904a8f33be48aaa7f09f23fa3\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z6dddefa904a8f33be48aaa7f09f23fa3\" data-section-id=\"bWWHP40\" data-sememe-id=\"gfbFlG\">stool cultures</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Sn0ysg&anker=Z429d21670093a08ffb061528b0561719\" data-learningcard-id=\"Sn0ysg\" data-anker=\"Z429d21670093a08ffb061528b0561719\" data-section-id=\"H0cKha0\" data-sememe-id=\"XjY9_K\">Clostridioides difficile</a> toxin assay. The absence of malabsorptive features makes <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=z80r63&anker=Z9aa32f677362a235a8ae39e011711f1b\" data-learningcard-id=\"z80r63\" data-anker=\"Z9aa32f677362a235a8ae39e011711f1b\" data-sememe-id=\"yzYdv7\">SIBO</a> unlikely.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=km0mfg&anker=Z168b3d17f93422e412d2868bdae5f50c\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-anker=\"Z168b3d17f93422e412d2868bdae5f50c\" data-section-id=\"F8bgov\" data-sememe-id=\"dOaork\">Budesonide</a> is a <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=km0mfg&anker=Z3733d22ef7bb87f743207060acda0451\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-anker=\"Z3733d22ef7bb87f743207060acda0451\" data-section-id=\"Pq1WA30\" data-sememe-id=\"8AbOlw\">corticosteroid</a> used for active <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VS0GA2&anker=Z4272f924349255b3e4babe86d4e939c9\" data-learningcard-id=\"VS0GA2\" data-anker=\"Z4272f924349255b3e4babe86d4e939c9\" data-section-id=\"Ow0IQR\" data-sememe-id=\"Wj0Pzf\">inflammatory bowel disease</a>. This patient has no active inflammation on <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=T806N3&anker=Za4aebc8baa131b83620292e8d0363739\" data-learningcard-id=\"T806N3\" data-anker=\"Za4aebc8baa131b83620292e8d0363739\" data-sememe-id=\"nWb7Ns\">colonoscopy</a>, and the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-sememe-id=\"ro0fWS\">diarrhea</a> is likely due to <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Q60ukS&anker=Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-learningcard-id=\"Q60ukS\" data-anker=\"Z86b474a966e0cc8faf1092967eaf82f4\" data-section-id=\"2FcThV0\" data-sememe-id=\"QOXuHy\">bile acid</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=0S0ey2&anker=Zae07822252537d684eeec3f2d4ba9adb\" data-learningcard-id=\"0S0ey2\" data-anker=\"Zae07822252537d684eeec3f2d4ba9adb\" data-sememe-id=\"n407PT\">malabsorption</a> from <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=eJ0xGS&anker=Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-learningcard-id=\"eJ0xGS\" data-anker=\"Zf3a10de88f22b839a2769aa9ae031960\" data-section-id=\"FzcguU0\" data-sememe-id=\"w4chlc0\">ileal</a> resection, not an inflammatory flare. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=km0mfg&anker=Z168b3d17f93422e412d2868bdae5f50c\" data-learningcard-id=\"km0mfg\" data-anker=\"Z168b3d17f93422e412d2868bdae5f50c\" data-section-id=\"F8bgov\" data-sememe-id=\"dOaork\">Budesonide</a> does not address <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Q60ukS&anker=Z2d717efa9ad0734fdb6828be1ec2a827\" data-learningcard-id=\"Q60ukS\" data-anker=\"Z2d717efa9ad0734fdb6828be1ec2a827\" data-section-id=\"2FcThV0\" data-sememe-id=\"G_cBpU0\">bile salt</a>–induced <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=6M0jpg&anker=Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-learningcard-id=\"6M0jpg\" data-anker=\"Z51b67b2885f849894721232a6bf6d273\" data-sememe-id=\"ro0fWS\">diarrhea</a>.</div>",
